Say hello to my little friend.
Scarface.

158
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,640
Get down, get to the chopper !

159
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,440
I gotta get to the chopper.

160
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,880
I'll be back.

161
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:30,240
I know it was you Fredo,
you broke my heart. Godfather 2.

162
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,680
Alright, alright, alright.

163
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,240
Alright, alright, alright.

164
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,760
Alright, alright, alright.

165
